    {
      "id": "stage-02",
      "order": 2,
      "title": "Cuadriláteros",
      "html": "<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"es\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>Cuadriláteros</title>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.css\">\n  <script defer src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.js\"></script>\n  <script defer src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js\"></script>\n  <style>\n    body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; padding: 1rem; }\n    h1, h2, h3 { margin: 0.2em 0; }\n    .badge { display:inline-block; font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 999px; background:#eef; margin-right: .4rem; }\n    .example, .task { border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.8rem; margin: 0.8rem 0; }\n    .note { font-size: .9rem; color:#333; background:#fafafa; padding:.6rem .8rem; border-left: 3px solid #ddd; border-radius:6px; }\n    .tip { background: #f0fbff; border-left: 4px solid #6ac8ff; padding: 10px 12px; margin: 14px 0; }\n    .grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px,1fr)); gap: 14px; }\n    .card { border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px; text-align:center; }\n    .card .label { font-weight: 700; color: #4338ca; margin: 0.3rem 0 0; }\n    .card .desc { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #555; margin: 0.2rem 0; }\n    svg { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display:block; margin: 8px auto; }\n    .step { margin:.3rem 0; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <h1>Cuadriláteros</h1>\n  <p><span class=\"badge\">5.º grado</span><span class=\"badge\">Geometría</span></p>\n\n  <p>Los <strong>cuadriláteros</strong> son polígonos de <strong>4 lados</strong>. La suma de sus ángulos interiores es siempre:</p>\n  $$\\alpha + \\beta + \\gamma + \\delta = 360°$$\n\n  <h2>Paralelogramos</h2>\n  <p>Son cuadriláteros cuyos lados opuestos son <strong>paralelos</strong> entre sí.</p>\n\n  <div class=\"grid\">\n    <!-- Cuadrado -->\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 120 120\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\">\n        <rect x=\"10\" y=\"10\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#4f46e5\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <rect x=\"10\" y=\"90\" width=\"12\" height=\"12\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#e11d48\" stroke-width=\"1\" />\n        <text x=\"55\" y=\"125\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">a</text>\n        <text x=\"2\" y=\"65\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\">a</text>\n      </svg>\n      <p class=\"label\">Cuadrado</p>\n      <p class=\"desc\">4 lados iguales<br/>4 ángulos rectos</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Rectángulo -->\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 160 110\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"140\" height=\"95\">\n        <rect x=\"10\" y=\"10\" width=\"140\" height=\"90\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0891b2\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <rect x=\"10\" y=\"80\" width=\"12\" height=\"12\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#e11d48\" stroke-width=\"1\" />\n        <text x=\"80\" y=\"118\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">b</text>\n        <text x=\"2\" y=\"58\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\">a</text>\n      </svg>\n      <p class=\"label\">Rectángulo</p>\n      <p class=\"desc\">Lados opuestos iguales<br/>4 ángulos rectos</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Rombo -->\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 140 130\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"120\" height=\"110\">\n        <polygon points=\"70,10 130,65 70,120 10,65\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#7c3aed\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <text x=\"36\" y=\"35\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\">a</text>\n        <text x=\"100\" y=\"35\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\">a</text>\n      </svg>\n      <p class=\"label\">Rombo</p>\n      <p class=\"desc\">4 lados iguales<br/>Ángulos opuestos iguales</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Romboide -->\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 170 110\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"150\" height=\"95\">\n        <polygon points=\"40,10 160,10 130,100 10,100\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#16a34a\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <text x=\"95\" y=\"8\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">b</text>\n        <text x=\"15\" y=\"60\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\">a</text>\n      </svg>\n      <p class=\"label\">Romboide</p>\n      <p class=\"desc\">Lados opuestos iguales<br/>Ángulos opuestos iguales</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <h2>Trapecios</h2>\n  <p>Cuadriláteros con <strong>un solo par</strong> de lados paralelos (las bases).</p>\n\n  <div class=\"grid\">\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 170 110\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"150\" height=\"95\">\n        <polygon points=\"50,15 120,15 150,95 20,95\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#f97316\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n        <text x=\"85\" y=\"10\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">base menor</text>\n        <text x=\"85\" y=\"112\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#555\" text-anchor=\"middle\">base mayor</text>\n      </svg>\n      <p class=\"label\">Trapecio</p>\n      <p class=\"desc\">Solo dos lados paralelos</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <h2>Trapezoides</h2>\n  <p>Cuadriláteros que <strong>no tienen</strong> ningún par de lados paralelos.</p>\n\n  <div class=\"grid\">\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 160 120\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"140\" height=\"105\">\n        <polygon points=\"60,10 140,30 120,110 15,90\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#dc2626\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n      </svg>\n      <p class=\"label\">Trapezoide</p>\n      <p class=\"desc\">Ningún lado paralelo</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"example\">\n    <h4>Ejemplo</h4>\n    <p>Un cuadrilátero tiene tres ángulos de $85°$, $110°$ y $95°$. ¿Cuánto mide el cuarto ángulo?</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">$\\delta = 360° - 85° - 110° - 95° = 70°$</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"note\">\n    <strong>Recuerda:</strong> Todo cuadrado es un rectángulo (y un rombo), pero no todo rectángulo es un cuadrado. Los paralelogramos forman una familia donde unos incluyen a otros.\n  </div>\n\n  <script>\n  document.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", function() {\n    renderMathInElement(document.body, {\n      delimiters: [{left: \"$$\", right: \"$$\", display: true},{left: \"$\", right: \"$\", display: false}]\n    });\n  });\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>",
      "formulas": [
        "\\alpha + \\beta + \\gamma + \\delta = 360°"
      ],
      "assets": []
