    {
      "id": "stage-03",
      "order": 3,
      "title": "Ángulos en polígonos",
      "html": "<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"es\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>Ángulos en polígonos</title>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.css\">\n  <script defer src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.js\"></script>\n  <script defer src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js\"></script>\n  <style>\n    body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; padding: 1rem; }\n    h1, h2, h3 { margin: 0.2em 0; }\n    .badge { display:inline-block; font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 999px; background:#eef; margin-right: .4rem; }\n    .example, .task { border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.8rem; margin: 0.8rem 0; }\n    .note { font-size: .9rem; color:#333; background:#fafafa; padding:.6rem .8rem; border-left: 3px solid #ddd; border-radius:6px; }\n    .tip { background: #f0fbff; border-left: 4px solid #6ac8ff; padding: 10px 12px; margin: 14px 0; }\n    .grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px,1fr)); gap: 14px; }\n    .card { border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px; text-align:center; }\n    svg { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display:block; margin: 8px auto; }\n    .step { margin:.3rem 0; }\n    table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 1rem 0; }\n    th, td { border: 1px solid #d1d5db; padding: 0.5rem 0.8rem; text-align: center; }\n    th { background: #eef2ff; color: #3730a3; }\n    tr:nth-child(even) { background: #f9fafb; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <h1>Ángulos en polígonos</h1>\n  <p><span class=\"badge\">5.º grado</span><span class=\"badge\">Geometría</span></p>\n\n  <h2>Fórmula general</h2>\n  <p>La suma de los ángulos interiores de cualquier polígono de $n$ lados se calcula con:</p>\n  $$\\text{Suma de ángulos interiores} = (n - 2) \\times 180°$$\n\n  <div class=\"tip\">\n    <strong>¿Por qué funciona?</strong> Desde un vértice de un polígono de $n$ lados podemos trazar $(n - 2)$ triángulos. Como cada triángulo suma $180°$, multiplicamos.\n  </div>\n\n  <svg viewBox=\"0 0 280 160\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"280\" height=\"160\">\n    <!-- Pentágono -->\n    <polygon points=\"140,15 230,65 210,150 70,150 50,65\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#4f46e5\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" />\n    <!-- Diagonales desde un vértice -->\n    <line x1=\"140\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"70\" y2=\"150\" stroke=\"#e11d48\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,3\" />\n    <line x1=\"140\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"210\" y2=\"150\" stroke=\"#e11d48\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,3\" />\n    <!-- Etiquetas de triángulos -->\n    <text x=\"100\" y=\"70\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#e11d48\" font-weight=\"bold\">T1</text>\n    <text x=\"135\" y=\"110\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#e11d48\" font-weight=\"bold\">T2</text>\n    <text x=\"170\" y=\"70\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#e11d48\" font-weight=\"bold\">T3</text>\n    <text x=\"140\" y=\"155\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#4f46e5\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Pentágono: 3 triángulos = 3 × 180° = 540°</text>\n  </svg>\n\n  <h2>Tabla de referencia</h2>\n  <table>\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>Polígono</th>\n        <th>Lados ($n$)</th>\n        <th>Triángulos ($n-2$)</th>\n        <th>Suma de ángulos</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr><td>Triángulo</td><td>3</td><td>1</td><td>$180°$</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Cuadrilátero</td><td>4</td><td>2</td><td>$360°$</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Pentágono</td><td>5</td><td>3</td><td>$540°$</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Hexágono</td><td>6</td><td>4</td><td>$720°$</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Heptágono</td><td>7</td><td>5</td><td>$900°$</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Octógono</td><td>8</td><td>6</td><td>$1080°$</td></tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n\n  <h2>Ejercicios</h2>\n  <div class=\"task\">\n    <h4>Calcula la suma de los ángulos interiores:</h4>\n    <p class=\"step\">1. Un polígono de 9 lados (eneágono): $(9 - 2) \\times 180° =$ ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">2. Un polígono de 10 lados (decágono): $(10 - 2) \\times 180° =$ ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">3. Un polígono de 12 lados (dodecágono): $(12 - 2) \\times 180° =$ ___</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"task\">\n    <h4>Razonamiento:</h4>\n    <p class=\"step\">4. Si un polígono regular tiene ángulos interiores que suman $1440°$, ¿cuántos lados tiene?</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">Pista: despeja $n$ de $(n - 2) \\times 180° = 1440°$</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">5. ¿Cuánto mide cada ángulo interior de un hexágono regular?</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">Pista: divide la suma entre el número de ángulos.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"note\">\n    <strong>Respuestas:</strong> 1) $1260°$ · 2) $1440°$ · 3) $1800°$ · 4) $n = 10$ lados · 5) $720° \\div 6 = 120°$\n  </div>\n\n  <script>\n  document.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", function() {\n    renderMathInElement(document.body, {\n      delimiters: [{left: \"$$\", right: \"$$\", display: true},{left: \"$\", right: \"$\", display: false}]\n    });\n  });\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>",
      "formulas": [
        "(n - 2) \\times 180°"
      ],
      "assets": []
    }
  ]
}